### Area

admin/ui

### Describe the bug

When assigning multiple user profile attributes to the same attribute group then the attribute group list shows repeated entries for the attribute group - one for each attribute assigned to the group.

### Version

22.0.4+ (main snapshot)

### Expected behavior

Attribute group list should only not show duplicate groups.

### Actual behavior

![image](https://github.com/keycloak/keycloak/assets/314690/1c48cf39-3d68-478d-b415-5f30bdc6a492)

Multiple group entries shown in attribute group list:
![image](https://github.com/keycloak/keycloak/assets/314690/b9c21985-f612-4732-8922-b4e4e636805b)


### How to Reproduce?

1) enable declarative-user-profile
2) Create a user profile as shown below
3) Look at the attribute group list

User Profile:
```
